import React from 'react'
import { InfoContainer, InfoContent, Heading } from './InfoElements'

const InfoSection = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <InfoContainer id='about'>
                <InfoContent>
                    <Heading>About Me</Heading>
                </InfoContent>
            </InfoContainer>  
        </>
    )
}

export default InfoSection
